name: Isleward Gaming
tagline: A collection of useful links for Isleward Gaming group
body:
### Welcome
Hi, this is a a small page that hosts useful links for games we play. Pull Requests are open if you wish to add stuff.

### Elite: Dangerous
[http://inara.cz/](http://inara.cz/) - Elite companion, shows market info, galaxy info, also serves as a CMDR log

[http://www.elitetradingtool.co.uk/](http://www.elitetradingtool.co.uk/) - A trading tool

[https://coriolis.io/](https://coriolis.io/) - A handy ship build/layout tool
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
